Package: rcaiman
Type: Package
Title: rcaiman: An R package for CAnopy IMage ANalysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Gaston Mauro Diaz 
Maintainer: Gaston Mauro Diaz <gastonmaurodiaz@gmail.com>
Description: The 'rcaiman' provide algorithms specially developed to classify 
    photographs of the plant canopy. It particularly cover hemispherical 
    photography and restricted view photography.
